Write a program to check whether a number is Even or Odd.
ans:
import java.util.*;
public class Java3{
public static void main(String args[]){
Scanner s=new Scanner(System.in);
System.out.print("Enter the Numbers:");
int a=s.nextInt();
if(a%2==0){
System.out.print("The number is even");
}
else{
System.out.println7
("the number is odd");
}
}
}
